Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Regex patterns not matching

Solution: Test patterns individually using re.search() in Python REPL
Verify input format matches expected pattern
Issue: JSON parsing errors

Solution: Validate JSON syntax using python3 -m json.tool < file.log
Check for trailing commas or malformed strings
Issue: Validator shows false positives

Solution: Review masked format - ensure it doesn't match detection patterns
Adjust masking to use non-numeric characters (X instead of *)
Issue: Hash collisions or inconsistent hashing

Solution: Ensure same salt/algorithm used consistently
Verify patient_id is string before hashing
